      "writtenOn": "2020-09-28T13:45:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ok, then please at least check git_common.IsFromCIPD(gitAbsPath).  Multiple critical git vulnerabilities have demonstrated the importance of asserting that we\u0027re using the correct git version.",
